data.description: Discover the untapped potential of this 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom single-story home in the prestigious Broken Sound Country Club in Boca Raton. With soaring ceilings in the living room, a beautifully updated kitchen, and a large primary suite, this property is a canvas waiting for a visionary owner. Embrace the Florida lifestyle with a spacious screened-in patio and a fully fenced yard offering privacy and security. Located in a community renowned for its award-winning golf course and a brand-new state-of-the-art clubhouse with world-class amenities, this residence invites you to reimagine and redefine luxury living. Seize the opportunity to transform this diamond in the rough into your dream home, leveraging the exclusivity of the Broken Sound Country Club backdrop.
